<div class="panel-inner">
  <h2 class="panel-title">About Me</h2>

  <div class="about-layout">
    <div class="about-body">
      <p>
        I'm Ofer — a data scientist and project manager with deep roots in geospatial systems. I combine
        analytical thinking, hands-on technical work, and the ability to lead teams and projects from
        concept to delivery. My work sits at the intersection of data, technology, and real-world impact.
      </p>
      <p>
        On the data side, I work with large, complex datasets — cleaning, modelling, and extracting
        insights using Python, SQL, and machine learning. Much of that work has been rooted in urban
        mobility: understanding how people move through cities, and what infrastructure and policy changes
        actually shift behaviour. My Master's thesis at Tel Aviv University analysed over one million
        shared e-scooter rides to quantify the effect of cycling infrastructure on rider behaviour —
        sharpening both my data science craft and my ability to turn findings into actionable recommendations.
      </p>
      <p>
        On the project side, I lead. I currently manage national-scale Spatial Data Infrastructure (SDI)
        programmes in Zanzibar and Ogun State, Nigeria — coordinating developers, government stakeholders,
        and technical teams across multiple time zones. I own the full lifecycle: requirements gathering,
        system architecture, delivery, and knowledge transfer to ensure clients can sustain what we build.
      </p>
      <p>
        Geospatial technology is the domain I know best, but the skills I lean on most — structured
        problem-solving, data-driven decision making, and getting diverse teams aligned around a goal —
        travel well beyond any single field.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-sidebar">
      <div class="skills-section">
        <h3 class="skills-title">Tech Stack</h3>
        <div class="chips">
          <span class="chip">QGIS</span>
          <span class="chip">ArcGIS</span>
          <span class="chip">PostgreSQL / PostGIS</span>
          <span class="chip">Python</span>
          <span class="chip">Pandas</span>
          <span class="chip">GeoPandas</span>
          <span class="chip">Leaflet</span>
          <span class="chip">NetworkX</span>
          <span class="chip">scikit-learn</span>
          <span class="chip">GeoServer</span>
          <span class="chip">GeoNode</span>
          <span class="chip">GDAL</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="skills-divider" />

      <div class="skills-section">
        <h3 class="skills-title">Soft Skills</h3>
        <div class="chips">
          <span class="chip chip-soft">Project Management</span>
          <span class="chip chip-soft">Team Leading</span>
          <span class="chip chip-soft">Agile Development Management</span>
          <span class="chip chip-soft">Technical Documentation</span>
          <span class="chip chip-soft">Long-term Planning</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.about-layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 240px;
  gap: 0;
}

.about-body {
  padding-right: 40px;
}
.about-body p {
  font-size: 0.975rem;
  line-height: 1.85;
  color: var(--ct-muted);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.about-body p:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.about-sidebar {
  padding-left: 32px;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--ct-border);
}

.skills-section {
  padding: 4px 0;
}

.skills-title {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ct-accent);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.chips {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
}

.chip {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--ct-muted);
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.skills-divider {
  border: none;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--ct-border);
  margin: 20px 0;
}

@media (max-width: 760px) {
  .about-layout {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .about-body {
    padding-right: 0;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ct-border);
    padding-bottom: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .about-sidebar {
    padding-left: 0;
    border-left: none;
  }
}
</style>
